 ● 🏗 Architecture

   ```
   crucible/
   ├── crates/
   │   ├── crucible-cli/      # CLI commands
   │   ├── crucible-core/     # Core types
   │   └── crucible-daemon/   # Background daemon
   ├── docs/                  # Documentation
   └── plugins/              # Example plugins
   ```

   🚀 Quick Commands

   ```bash
   # Install
   curl -fsSL https://example.com/install.sh | sh
   ```

   ```bash
   # Chat with AI
   cru chat

   # Start MCP server
   cru mcp
   ```

   📊 Comparison

   ┌──────────────────────┬────────────────┬───────┐
   │ Feature              │ Crucible       │ Other │
   ├──────────────────────┼────────────────┼───────┤
   │ Local-first          │ ✅             │ ❌    │
   ├──────────────────────┼────────────────┼───────┤
   │ Sessions as markdown │ ✅             │ ❌    │
   ├──────────────────────┼────────────────┼───────┤
   │ Semantic search      │ ✅ Block-level │ ❌    │
   └──────────────────────┴────────────────┴───────┘
                                                                                
